                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The dread wraith extends its hand toward another wraith creature within 100 feet. The target wraith dissolves and streaks toward the dread wraith in a straight line, dealing [[/r 6d10[negative]]] damage to each creature along the line (@Check[type:fortitude|dc:28|basic:true] save).</p>\n<p>The dread wraith absorbs the essence of the target wraith, becoming @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Quickened]{Quickened} and gaining a +10-foot status bonus to its fly Speed for a number of rounds equal to the level of the absorbed wraith. It can use its extra action only to Fly or Strike.</p>\n<p>An unwilling target can attempt a @Check[type:will|dc:28] save to resist being absorbed.</p>"
                },
